&gt;Subject: [junit] Implementing JUnit AFTER development has started...
&gt;
&gt;Does anyone have any opinions, suggestions or approaches as to how to best 
&gt;implement JUnit AFTER development has started?  We have a significant code 
&gt;base already and we&#39;re trying to move to JUnit.  What issues did you have 
&gt;when trying this yourself?  Was your testing hierarchy exactly the same as 
&gt;your application package structure?  Did you start only using JUnit with 
&gt;new development or with bugs as well?  Or did you take a month off and 
&gt;have everyone write JUnit tests?  Any help would be greatly appreciated.
&gt;
&gt;
&gt;-dmg
